Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,柚姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,稔、柚姬谈论
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,非常像ちぃ的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.28,0:01:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不太像是恶作剧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后还有其他\N与寄图者有关的线索吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不，暂时还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,柚姬你不需要道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再确认一次看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,能调出收到这张图当天的资料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,也许会发现些什么也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这…这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這張照片怎麼看都像是ちぃ對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,虽…虽然不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不過看起來很像ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这堆乱七八糟的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没看过这种接头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会是恶作剧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在某處看過ちぃ的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,先拍下她的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然后合成出这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不过总觉得其中并不单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,被手郲住的这个字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是“ C ”的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,C、H、O、B、I、T …
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Chobits
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前应该跟你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,以“ Chobits ”为代号的\N那台传说中的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,能够自己思考行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有人的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,却又不是人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這張照片是ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那果然是恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没必要操这个心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯，ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ就是ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ自己也不記得這張圖片…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,其实根本谈不上什么记忆\N因为资料跟OS都不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,稔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,能否让我插句话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,重新查詢看看\Nちぃ至今做過的事如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也許會發現\Nちぃ與圖片的關連性也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和，你问她一下电话号码
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,先别管那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，你知道我的电话号码吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,03-68828-52DF3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她说话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次講出“ちぃ”以外的字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她有安装学习软件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她是被丢在垃圾堆里，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会是在被丢掉前初始化了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是这样\N但学习机能却还留着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果好好教她\N我想她不但能够说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也能够做其他事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你好好教她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她现在的主人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她会按 照你教她的方式行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼了？ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,幽会时的暗号遭到利用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,惨遭妻子杀害的女人怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,至今仍徘徊在那间公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在跟她遇害当天\N同样的闷热阴天里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她就会发出那个暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,男人以前所用的幽会暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,将房间的电灯关了又开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,关了又开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在那里等待着新的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在G公寓的104号房里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那间不应该有的104号房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你啊，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那个鬼故事\N说的果然就是 GAB 城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那就一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,去 GAB 城崎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去上面看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有…有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,身…身体动不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ，不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快动，快动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ…ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,仓库？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因为最近东西容易发霉潮湿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,原本想来个大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可是电灯泡快要坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一直没办法打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为了换灯泡\N我找来了各种东西垫脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我还是碰不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才会叫我来帮忙换
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可是从门下面\N流出的黑色液体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，我搬桌子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不小心打翻了水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候我有上去找本须和帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你看起来好像很忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,电灯泡、桌子、水桶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不过为什么会有104号房？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看来一楼本来有四间房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,隔壁是103号房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我搬来时做了一点改装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,缺的是102号房
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然被搞得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真是丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不害怕了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大魔王终于登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙是打不倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他那么强吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我看杂志和网路上的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还没看过有人打倒过他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,警告，警告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,通过这里就可以到下个城镇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，你是认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,别想不开了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你是打不赢那家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ她也許正在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,真是拿他没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,丝茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,carbonara
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,chorizo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不行了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ち…ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,當時ちぃ明明沒有經驗值
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,却打倒了游戏里的大魔王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和也不可能会写这种程式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,难道她真的不是普通的电脑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚那个你有看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树看到海豚的“哗啦”\N会很高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ也要來嘩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是不会游泳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,ち…ちぃ呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,从表面看来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好像也没进水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树，你在生气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ做錯事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会生气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,秀树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她真是台不可思议的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一般如果掉到海里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就会进水，然后会很难修复
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ちぃ的相關記憶資料到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,光靠我们果然还是\N有点资料不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,找新保帮忙看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不过新保少爷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,新保，新保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天先出门了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好严重的黑眼圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,熬夜了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像也很困的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,清…清水老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这么晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,让我住一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,突然叫那么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,大家回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要开始上课了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,清水老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,清水老师还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有时会早到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可是她从来没迟到过的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我接通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个声音，你是新保对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在在搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,跟老师私奔…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们吵架了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很久没有吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,或者应该说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,连话都说不上两句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,上了门链就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我老公忘了我会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在不在家都没影响了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:18:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就觉得怎样都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得怎样都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明明在说这么伤心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她却没有哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她其实很想哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,只是拼命在忍耐罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想至少让她在遇到\N不愉快或伤心的事时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能够哭个痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我迷上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此，为什么要私奔？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,难道只剩这个方法了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们这个年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还是小鬼而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,以后你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.77,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也许就如同你所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这是我的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,决定？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,多香子她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,变得不相信男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,她认为就算一开始说喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦出现像电脑那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可以迎合自己的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.23,0:19:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就会完全改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好像从没喜欢过一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不让她跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,决定私奔到深山的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个好地方喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样湿答答的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那不过是旅行而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,恩恩爱爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说，这算是私奔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在多香子点头之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,点头？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我再婚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,再婚，再婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再婚是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,丝茉茉再帮我保管一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,帮你保管当然没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拜罗，本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我会再跟你联络的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再有什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要告诉我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,本须和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这种重考生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,帮不了你太大的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不过或许我可以帮上什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.22,0:20:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要告诉我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一定喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,像电脑那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可以迎合自己的对象啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,稔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,您还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，让我帮您泡杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.65,0:20:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还是休息一下比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我这并不是累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我當時分析ちぃ沒失敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,假使这孩子学会了说话\N学会了做各种不同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,纵使她再怎么乖巧\N再怎么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,劝你还是别喜欢上她比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不想在日后\N伤心流泪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,稔少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,口味…不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我是用跟姊姊同样的方法泡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很好喝
